1. *Dim* se širi sobom. (Smoke *spreads* around the room.)
2. U zatvorenoj prostoriji ne bi smelo biti *dim*a. (There shouldn't be any *smoke* in a closed room.)
3. *Dim* se digao u nebo. (The *smoke* rose up to the sky.)
4. Dugme za paljenje i gašenje *dim*a je na zidu. (The button for turning on and off the *smoke* is on the wall.)
5. Vatra je izazvala gust *dim*. (The fire caused thick *smoke*.)
6. Miris *dim*a me podseća na detinjstvo. (The smell of *smoke* reminds me of childhood.)
7. *Dim* se širi iz dimnjaka. (The *smoke* is spreading from the chimney.)
8. Kroz *dim* nije bilo lako videti. (It wasn't easy to see through the *smoke*.)
9. Kuvanje bez *dim*a je moguće uz dobar ventilacioni sistem. (Cooking without *smoke* is possible with a good ventilation system.)
10. Upalio je sveću i uživao u njenom *dim*u. (He lit a candle and enjoyed its *smoke*.)